\displaystyle lim_{x\to0}\frac{2xcos(2x)}{sin(2x)}\neq 0
lim_{x\to0}\frac{2xcos(2x)}{sin(2x)}=lim_{x\to0}\frac{2cos(2x)-2xsin(2x)}{2cos(2x)}=lim_{x\to0} 1-2xtg(2x)=1+0=1
\lim\limits_{x\to 0}\left(\frac{1+x\sin(2x)-\cos(x)}{\sin^2(x)}\right)=\lim\limits_{x\to 0}\frac{\sin(2x)}{\sin(2x)}+\frac{2x\cos(2x)}{\sin(2x)}+\frac{\sin(x)}{\sin(2x)}
 = 1+\frac 1 2+1=\frac 5 2
